    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Balto.</placeName>
                <date>June 4th 1857</date>.</p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Revd. Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Dear Sir—</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">I had this pleasure yester-<lb/>day in registered letter, with
                enclosure $109.96/100,<lb/> in full of accot. Referring to my remarks<lb/> in same I
                give below a copy of the statement<lb/> handed me by <persName>Dr.
                    Guinsburg</persName></p>
            <table cols="3" rows="17">
                <row>
                    <cell>
                        <persName>Mr Is. Leeser</persName>
                    </cell>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell>Cr</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>For 2 doz. Readers @</cell>
                    <cell>$4.__</cell>
                    <cell>$8.00</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>“ 2 “ <persName>Nath</persName> “ “</cell>
                    <cell>2.40</cell>
                    <cell>4.80</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>“ 2 “ <persName>Pix.</persName> Quest. “</cell>
                    <cell>4.80</cell>
                    <cell>9.60</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>“ 1 “ Catechisms “</cell>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell>6.—</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>“ 1 “ Prayer Book</cell>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell>
                        <hi rend="underline"> 2.—</hi>
                    </cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell>$30.40</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell>Dr</cell>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell><persName>Mr Cohen</persName>, for him returned</cell>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>18 Readers</cell>
                    <cell>$6.—</cell>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>18 <persName>Nath.</persName> Readers</cell>
                    <cell>3.60</cell>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>19 <persName>Pix.</persName> Quest.</cell>
                    <cell>7.60</cell>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>11 Catechisms</cell>
                    <cell>5.50</cell>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>1 Prayer Book</cell>
                    <cell>
                        <hi rend="underline">2.—</hi>
                    </cell>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell>$24.70</cell>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>To Commo.10%</cell>
                    <cell>—.57</cell>
                    <cell>25.27</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell>Sold</cell>
                    <cell>5.13/100</cell>
                </row>
            </table>
            <p>I find some difference between his statement<lb/> as handed me, &amp; the number of
                books handed me.</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <table cols="3" rows="6">
                <row>
                    <cell role="label"/>
                    <cell role="label"><persName>Dr. G's</persName> a/c calls for</cell>
                    <cell role="label">The numbers handed me</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>Readers</cell>
                    <cell>18</cell>
                    <cell>18</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell><persName>Nath.</persName> Readers</cell>
                    <cell>18</cell>
                    <cell>19</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell><persName>Pix.</persName> Questions</cell>
                    <cell>19</cell>
                    <cell>17</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>Catechisms</cell>
                    <cell>11</cell>
                    <cell>11</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>Prayer Book</cell>
                    <cell>
                        <hi rend="underline">1</hi>
                    </cell>
                    <cell>
                        <hi rend="underline">1</hi>
                    </cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell>67 Books</cell>
                    <cell>66 Books</cell>
                </row>
            </table>
            <p>The differences amounts to but little, but I will<lb/> see him and have it put right.
                I have the<lb/> Books in my possession &amp; will do with them<lb/> as you may
                direct. Expecting to hear from<lb/> you soon I remain</p>
            <p rend="indent(10)">Very Resptfy</p>
            <p rend="indent(10)">
                <persName role="author">Edward Cohen</persName>
            </p>
        </body>
